examples.en: Her foot was drumming on the carpet.
I could hear the rain drumming against the windows.
I bet Stive's been drumming every room in the joint.
He had an annoying habit of drumming his fingers on the table while he listened.
We could hear a rhythmic drumming outside.
Perot was in Europe, drumming up business for his new investment company.
He travelled throughout Latin America drumming up support for the confederation.
